Shortly after the [[Great Hyperspace War/Legends|Great Hyperspace War]], the [[Empress Teta system/Legends|Empress Teta system]] succumbed to a more military-minded government, which led to a rise in popularity of the '''Cinnagar war suit'''. It was a highly-capable example of battle [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that continued to be used at least until the time of the [[Jedi Civil War]] and in years afterward.

